<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.7.6">
<l>maḻuviyal paṭaiyuṭai yavaṉiṭam maḻaimukil</l>
<l>taḻuviya vuruviṉar tirumakaḷ maruviya</l>
<l>koḻuviya ceḻumalar muḻuciya paṟavaipaṇ</l>
<l>eḻuviya kaṇapura maṭikaḷta miṭamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of the one with the weapon formed as an axe,</l>
<l>The one whose appearance embraces [that of] a rain cloud,</l>
<l>The place of god is Kaṇṇapuram where swell the melodies of winged [bees]</l>
<l>Which dove into the luxuriant flowers where lady Tiru appears</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] were trapped.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
